# Entity service colors (user portal)

Subtle **transport / freight / warehouse** identity on user portal content — **not** status pills, route chips, sidebar accent, or primary buttons.

## Source of truth

| Piece | Path |
|-------|------|
| Base hues + derived tokens | `src/styles/_entity-service-accent.scss` (imported in `styles.scss`) |
| Host class helper | `shared/constants/entity-context-class.ts` → `entityContextClass(tab)` → `entity-context--{transport\|freight\|warehouse}` |
| Type | `UserEntityTab` in `shared/constants/user-urls.ts` |

**Current bases** (change only in `_entity-service-accent.scss`):

| Service | Light | Dark |
|---------|-------|------|
| Transport | `#0e7490` (vivid cyan) | `#06b6d4` |
| Freight | `#ea580c` | `#fed7aa` |
| Warehouse | `#a21caf` | `#f0abfc` |

Transport uses **stronger** spine/icon/filter mixes (override in `.entity-context--transport`) — avoid pale blues that blend into `--bg-app` / `--bg-surface`.

## Do not use for

- `StatusBadgeComponent` / `--status-*` (workflow only)
- Route chips (`--chip-neutral-*`)
- `--portal-accent` (sidebar / guest login only)
- Full card backgrounds or primary CTAs

## UX pattern — “accent spine”

| State | Cards (intent, quick-action) |
|-------|------------------------------|
| Rest | **3px left spine** + **colored icon** (`--entity-accent-icon`) |
| Hover / focus | Stronger spine, `--entity-accent-border`, `--entity-accent-hover-bg`, shadow |

Icons + labels remain required (color-blind safe).

## Components with optional `entityTab`

| Component | Input | When to set |
|-----------|-------|-------------|
| `IntentCardComponent` | `entityTab` | Home journey, Offer picker |
| `QuickActionCardComponent` | `entityTab`, `queryParams?` | User home quick actions; **omit** on admin dashboard (neutral) |
| `PageTitleComponent` | `entityTab` | User entity create/edit + detail pages |
| `DataTableComponent` | `entityTab` | User embedded hub tables (`table-all/`, `table-our/`) |
| `EntityTabsComponent` | (active tab) | Applies `entity-context--*` on **active** pill only |

Apply class via `entityContextClass()` or host/`ngClass` — do not hardcode hex in component SCSS.

## Hub tables (`DataTableComponent`)

When `entityTab` is set on host:

- Filter toolbar: **always** `2px` top + `3px` left `--entity-filter-accent` (not only when filters active)
- Row / mobile card hover: `--entity-accent-row-hover`
- Mobile row cards: left spine at rest

Table entity chrome lives in `_entity-service-accent.scss` (global) to stay within component SCSS budget.

## User home (`portal/user/features/home/`)

Order: **snapshot** → **quick actions** → **journey** → browse footer.

| Section | Widget | Config |
|---------|--------|--------|
| Quick actions | `QuickActionCardComponent` | `home.actions.config.ts` — 3×2 grid (Find + Offer per entity); admin-style panel SCSS; desktop subgrid for equal card heights |
| Journey | `IntentCardComponent` | `journeyGroups` in `home-page.component.ts` — scenario cards with `[entityTab]` |

Quick action titles: `portal.user.nav.findTransport|findFreight|findWarehouse` + `offerTransport|…`. Descriptions: `portal.user.features.home.actions.*.description`.

## i18n

- `portal.user.features.home.quickActions.title`
- `portal.user.features.home.actions.find*.description` / `offer*.description`
- `portal.user.features.home.journey.*` (journey cards unchanged)
- `portal.user.nav.findTransport|findFreight|findWarehouse`

## Adding a fourth service type

1. Extend `UserEntityTab` + `USER_ENTITY_TABS` in `user-urls.ts`
2. Add bases + `.entity-context--*` block in `_entity-service-accent.scss`
3. Wire tabs, home config, table pages, icons in `user-page-icons.ts`

